---
title: Ground Protein Meatballs and Savoury Thyme Gravy with Roasted Potatoes and Sugar Snap Peas
description: Plant-based meatballs, potatoes and gravy are a classic combo! Need we say more? The easy thyme-onion gravy makes tonight's plate rich and flavourful. This dish is timeless and perfect for any night of the week!
